e beneficial to your business.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Business cards help in separating business expenses from personal expenses. It also reduces paperwork and builds good credit history.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"money-market-accounts\"><\/span>Money Market Accounts<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Money market accounts offer small businesses a chance to gain interest using the money in their accounts. In addition to earning high-interest rates, these accounts are insured. These accounts reduce investing risks since they allow you full access to your money and withdraw without penalty.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, they come with restrictions on the number of transactions you can perform within a specific period.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"access-to-mobile-banking\"><\/span>Access to Mobile Banking<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Mobile banking is a major service that allows businesses to access banking services using a phone. Entrepreneurs can use banking app features to conduct their daily transactions. Some of the mobile banking features and benefits include;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Full access to information<\/li><li>Conduct financial transactions without necessarily visiting the bank<\/li><li>Offer support services such as loans and credit facilities<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"best-business-banking-features-and-tools-to-grow-your-business\"><\/span>Best Business Banking Features and Tools to Grow Your Business<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/digital-banking-1024x538.jpg\" alt=\"digital banking\" class=\"wp-image-764\" width=\"768\" height=\"404\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/digital-banking-1024x538.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/localhost:8