al advancement led to the upcoming online banks that brought in a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bain.com\/about\/media-center\/press-releases\/2018\/loyalty-in-banking\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">lot of competition<\/a> in the banking industry. Most physical banks had to launch <a href=\"https:\/\/verv.novatti.com\/the-pros-and-cons-of-online-banking\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">online banking<\/a> features to cope with clients\u2019 demands. Online banking has numerous advantages, especially when receiving or making international digital payments.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A <a href=\"https:\/\/www.fdic.gov\/analysis\/household-survey\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">study<\/a> conducted by FDIC found that 60% of people use online banking for digital payments and money transfers. Below are some of the main mobile banking features and benefits for businesses:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Low payment rates and fees<\/li><li>Provide better online experiences to clients<\/li><li>They have better and well-designed banking app features<\/li><li>Some of the main banking features and tools of online banking include:<br>Ability to open a fixed account<\/li><li>Paying bills such as rent, electricity, and water<\/li><li>Money transfer<\/li><li>Monitor account statements via the internet<\/li><li>Make digital payments<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/choose-the-best-online-business-banking-service\/\">Online payment services<\/a> are easy to use and can help grow your business. Most of them contain digital banking features that fit within your budget. It also offers multiple channels to pay employees, such as direct deposits, paper cheques, and digital payments through payment processors.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"account-software-integration\"><\/span>Account software Integration<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Accounting is an integral part of your business\u2019 operation. Accounting software is a basic program that helps you manage your accounting needs and provide detailed financial reports. As your business expands, the need to have a more sophisticated program grows. You require one to connect you to other systems and offer a two-way communication system.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A good program will reduce redundancy by putting together data from different systems. Software that can perform all these functions forms an essential part of your business. Account software integration has several benefits that include:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Better management of cash flow<\/li><li>Reduced overall costs spent on data input and payment of outsourced services<\/li><li>It provides access to real-time data<\/li><li>Enhances the productivity of employees as they concentrate on the relevant business task<\/li><li>Integrating your account software with a bank account also helps you monitor your cash flow in real-time. It automatically adds and deducts money moving in and out of your bank account.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"fraud-insurance\"><\/span>Fraud Insurance<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Fraud insurance is among the newest mobile banking features and benefits. Most banks include insurance services in their packages. It helps prevent the loss of money in the business checking account due to fraudulent transactions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Fraud insurance is essential for business accounts accessed by more than one person. It also reduces loss to accounts with several daily transactions. Fraud insurance prevents loss of money and protects any failed checks given by vendors, which can harm the business.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"are-you-looking-for-the-best-bank-for-your-business\"><\/span>Are You Looking For the Best Bank for your Business?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>One needs to perform detailed research before settling on any bank. Choosing a bank that offers services in line with your business is important. Some of the main features of innovative banking to look for include the availability of business credit cards, access to digital banking features, payroll solutions, and fraud insurance. A good bank will also offer a dedicated business banker to help manage your account.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>In Verv<\/strong> we are one of the latest brands that offer professional, reliable, and trustworthy digital banking features. We work with young and energetic employees who are always ready to help your business grow. We have some of the best banking features and tools well suited for any business.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Visit our <a href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/\">website<\/a> today and learn more about their mobile banking features and benefits.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Banks provide several services to ensure customer satisfaction. However, not all these services are business-oriented. The article below describes some of the main banking features and tools that will enable your business to thrive. <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":974,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[25,16,17],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/972"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=972"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/972\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":975,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/972\/revisions\/975"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp